name: Ext_R5_NamingSystem_version
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.NamingSystem.version for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents NamingSystem.version from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/NamingSystem|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4.

element.short: Business version of the naming system
element.definition: The identifier that is used to identify this version of the naming system when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or instance. This is an arbitrary value managed by the naming system author and is not expected to be globally unique. For example, it might be a timestamp (e.g. yyyymmdd) if a managed version is not available. There is also no expectation that versions can be placed in a lexicographical sequence.
